          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Nine 208 mu-g/cm2 targets with aluminium degrades",
                "in two different groups were irradiated.",
                "Targets were of Os natural composition (184Os -0.02%,",
                "186Os -1.58%, 187Os -1.6%, 188Os -13.3%,",
                "189Os -16.1%, 190Os -26.4%, 192Os -41.0%)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The gamma-spectrometry was carried out by",
                "50 cm3 HPGe detectors connected to multichannel",
                "analysers."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The decays of the different radionuclides have",
                "been followed for not less than three half-lives and",
                "the length of measurements were chosen for each",
                "radionuclide so that the counting statistical error on",
                "the photopeak areas was always of the order of less",
                "than 1%. The cumulative statistical error on each thin",
                "target yield data, due to errors on photopeak areas,",
                "decay constant, integrated charge and detector",
                "efficiency, was in total less than a few percent."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " uncertainty in the detector efficiency."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "EN-ERR",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Mean value between the incident beam energy",
                "and the outgoing beam energy (calculated using range",
                "and stopping-power TRIM91 code."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Systematic errors related to the stopping power",
                "calculations and the gamma-emission abundances were",
                "not taken into account.",
                "Radioactive growth-up was taken into account,",
                "adopting the proper correction equations of the",
                "radioactive chains (i.e., 188Pt/188Ir)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "STATUS": [
